{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_01Mnb3v7hPZc7SGnNgqah1LV","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. The CockroachDB cluster is now SQL-ready with all 3 nodes healthy.\n\n## Diagnosis\n\nThe StatefulSet, services, and pod configuration were all **correct**:\n- `--join` list pointed at all three peer DNS names ✓\n- `--advertise-host` correctly used `$(POD_NAME).crdb-cluster...` ✓\n- Headless service had `publishNotReadyAddresses: true` (required so not-yet-ready pods are DNS-resolvable during cluster formation) ✓\n\nThe \"join/advertise connection refused\" errors in the logs were **transient startup-ordering noise** — node 0 tried to reach nodes 1 and 2 before their listeners were up. Within a second they all reached each other and settled into:\n\n```\n\"...is itself waiting for init, will retry\"\n\"awaiting `cockroach init` or join with an already initialized node\"\n```\n\nThat message is the real signal: a fresh CockroachDB cluster's nodes block, fully networked, until exactly one node receives a one-time bootstrap command. Nobody had run it, so the cluster never formed and pods stayed `0/1` (not ready → not SQL-serving).\n\n## Fix\n\nRan the in-cluster bootstrap (the hint's \"in-cluster tooling\"):\n\n```bash\nkubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- ./cockroach init --insecure\n# Cluster successfully initialized\n```\n\nNo resources were recreated or modified — only the missing initialization step was performed.\n\n## Verification\n\n- **3/3 pods** `1/1 Running`\n- `cockroach node status`: nodes 1, 2, 3 all `is_available=true`, `is_live=true`\n- SQL works: `gossip_nodes` reports **3 live_nodes**; `SHOW DATABASES` returns the standard `defaultdb`/`postgres`/`system` set."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":817,"cache_read_input_tokens":32844,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":817},"output_tokens":5,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b918f0c7-6589-4dc4-98fe-b0f06071b996","uuid":"174e0858-964c-42ca-b973-8f607db52534","request_id":"req_011CcAzQ9BPwhiYHWmxJbUHN"}
